ActFederal Real Property and Federal Immovables Act
SubjectOrder Amending Order in Council P.C. 2015-1027 of June 23, 2015 and authorizing the grant of the Real property to Atomic Energy of Canada Limited
PrecisOrder (a) amending section 12 of the schedule to Order in Council P.C. 2015-1027 of June 23, 2015 by replacing the words, “All of PIN 2667-0040 (LT)” with “All of PIN 26672-0040 (LT)”; and (b) authorizing the grant of the real property to Atomic Energy of Canada Limited, as described in the schedule.
